data.description: Awesome townhouse featuring pantry, island, new granite counters, and new stainless steel appliances in the updated kitchen. Close to TQL stadium, OTR, and Washington Park! It has 3 bedrooms and an additional bedroom or office on the 1st floor with its own full bath!  Hardwood floors on the main floor with all new carpet in the bedrooms. Primary bedroom has a walk-in closet, double vanity, and large soaking tub. NEW Trex balcony deck. View of Laurel Park across the street. Includes Home warranty
